 door and sits on her bed with a loud sigh.","words":[[134,"Finally"],[135,"Bunu"],[136,"gets"],[137,"tired"],[138,"of"],[139,"waiting"],[140,"and"],[141,"waiting"],[142,"and"],[143,"waiting."],[144,"She"],[145,"unties"],[146,"the"],[147,"string"],[148,"from"],[149,"the"],[150,"door"],[151,"and"],[152,"sits"],[153,"on"],[154,"her"],[155,"bed"],[156,"with"],[157,"a"],[158,"loud"],[159,"sigh."]]},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55593/size6/40c057f229b09aedb234499bb2b6f91f.jpg","text":"Chunnu, her sister,\nwalks in after some time. “That was a terrible\nidea,” she says, pointing at the door. “Why don’t I pull the string, and your\ntooth will come out like that?”","words":[[160,"Chunnu,"],[161,"her"],[162,"sister,"],[163,"walks"],[164,"in"],[165,"after"],[166,"some"],[167,"time."],[168,"“That"],[169,"was"],[170,"a"],[171,"terrible"],[172,"idea,”"],[173,"she"],[174,"says,"],[175,"pointing"],[176,"at"],[177,"the"],[178,"door."],[179,"“Why"],[180,"don’t"],[181,"I"],[182,"pull"],[183,"the"],[184,"string,"],[185,"and"],[186,"your"],[187,"tooth"],[188,"will"],[189,"come"],[190,"out"],[191,"like"],[192,"that?”"]]},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55743/size6/4d8715d9fa312bf88aa60f2219402772.jpg","text":"Chunnu snapped her\nfingers.\n Bunu closes her eyes\nand opens her mouth.\n\"One, two,\nthree!\" Chunnu pulls.\n\"OWWW!” Bunu screams.\n\"It is not\nready,” Chunnu says.\n\"Wait for some time and\nit will fall out on its\nown.\"","words":[[193,"Chunnu"],[194,"snapped"],[195,"her"],[196,"fingers."],[197,"Bunu"],[198,"closes"],[199,"her"],[200,"eyes"],[201,"and"],[202,"opens"],[203,"her"],[204,"mouth."],[205,"\"One,"],[206,"two,"],[207,"three!\""],[208,"Chunnu"],[209,"pulls"],[210,"."],[211,"\"OWWW!”"],[212,"Bunu"],[213,"screams."],[214,"\"It"],[215,"is"],[216,"not"],[217,"ready,”"],[218,"Chunnu"],[219,"says."],[220,"\"Wait"],[221,"for"],[222,"some"],[223,"time"],[22