"stops"],[315,"and"],[316,"stares"],[317,"at"],[318,"her,"],[319,"then"],[320,"scurries"],[321,"away"],[322,"into"],[323,"a"],[324,"hole."]]},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55597/size6/19132335a991f45ab413f3a05117f8d5.jpg","text":"As soon as Bunu wakes up, she pushes the tooth with her tongue.\nBut there is nothing there!\nDid she swallow it? Did someone pull it out when she was sleeping? \nWhere is it?\nThere it is! Right next to the pillow. Bunu picks the tooth up and dashes outside.","words":[[325,"As"],[326,"soon"],[327,"as"],[328,"Bunu"],[329,"wakes"],[330,"up,"],[331,"she"],[332,"pushes"],[333,"the"],[334,"tooth"],[335,"with"],[336,"her"],[337,"tongue."],[338,"But"],[339,"there"],[340,"is"],[341,"nothing"],[342,"there!"],[343,"Did"],[344,"she"],[345,"swallow"],[346,"it?"],[347,"Did"],[348,"someone"],[349,"pull"],[350,"it"],[351,"out"],[352,"when"],[353,"she"],[354,"was"],[355,"sleeping?"],[356,"Where"],[357,"is"],[358,"it?"],[359,"There"],[360,"it"],[361,"is!"],[362,"Right"],[363,"next"],[364,"to"],[365,"the"],[366,"pillow."],[367,"Bunu"],[368,"picks"],[369,"the"],[370,"tooth"],[371,"up"],[372,"and"],[373,"dashes"],[374,"outside."]]},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55599/size6/ed38b3a54da9a3cab34249c85fef8c80.jpg","text":"“Musa, Musa, please\ntake my tooth \nand give me a new one!” she says.\nShe throws her\ntooth on the roof\nand runs back inside to tell Mama.","words":[[375,"“Musa,"],[376,"Musa,"],[377,"please"],[378,"take"],[379,"my"],[380,"tooth"],[381,"and"],[382,"give"],[383,"me"],[384,"a"],[385,"new"],[386,"one!”"],[387,"she"],[388,"says."],[389,"She"],[390,"throws"],[391,"her"],[392,"tooth"],[393,"on"],[394,"the"],[395,"roof"],[396,"and"],[397,"runs"],[398,"back"],[399,"inside"],[400,"to"],[401,"tell"],[402,"Mama."]]}],"stats":{"pages":12,"words":400}}